{"tid":470196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪低了]列香港台灣為國家惹強國網民公憤,MAMA急下架還道歉","createTime":"2017-11-16T05:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T05:47:21.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"092409a68e9d9de5e908e5d08d3c34b0b9d52fb7","tid":470196,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"南韓音樂盛會《MAMA》頒獎典禮原本在官網列出國家列表，供網友們投票，更把台灣從中國「分裂出去」，這完全激怒中國網友的玻璃心，而今，再度舉辦「道歉大賽」，MAMA於微博上道歉，並撤下「國家」的投票網站。<br />\n<br />\nMAMA於昨日晚間11點多在微博上公告：「對於大家的憂慮我們感同身受並深表歉意。目前相關網頁已經徹底刪除，以後我們會更加謹慎辦事以避免相關事件再次發生。再次深深感謝對MAMA給予關注的廣大網友。​​​​」現在MAMA官網上，只保留以藝人或團體為名的投票網站，以國家為列表的投票網已經被撤除。<br />\n<br />\n日前中國網友們對MAMA讓台港澳「獨立」紛紛表示：「國家領土完整必須維護，只有一個中國。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171116/1242134/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171116%2F1242134%2F&d=f5FGq3ggdxP5DuSvVviHgQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=95b4aa1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171116%2F1242134%2F&h=a63dbd6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171116/1242134/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171116/640_499bd1f581aaa355f414eca7694c575b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171116%2F640_499bd1f581aaa355f414eca7694c575b.jpg&h=c927f3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171116/640_e51c8cc7bbd05494b4acac5382532f7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171116%2F640_e51c8cc7bbd05494b4acac5382532f7b.jpg&h=73173f3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4fff17751d8365066aa3ad8d322589643a8000b","tid":470196,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"玻璃心碎"},{"pid":"46ccfa179b9e7c24aced3ffa04c898f5714b5300","tid